PrecisEnactment of REGULATIONS PRESCRIBING ALTERNATIVE MEANS OF PUBLICATION (FOREIGN COMPANIES) which provide that the information concerning foreign companies that is required by section 585 of the Act to be published in the Canada Gazette on a quarterly basis may instead be published on the Web site of the Office of the Superintendent of Financial Institutions.
